660
00:32:52,990 --> 00:32:54,340
Cái gã đóng con cua ấy?

661
00:32:54,430 --> 00:32:56,560


662
00:32:56,650 --> 00:32:58,820


663
00:32:58,910 --> 00:33:00,300
Cái thằng phía trước,
